  "texts": [
    "This difference in primary language often leads to communication between the deaf and hearing people relying solely on text.",
    "However, text-based communication is clearly inconvenient and inefficient.",
    "It is particularly challenging for children who have not yet learned written languages.",
    "Meanwhile, 90% deaf children grow up in homes where their parents are hearing people and do not use sign languages.",
    "3 This creates a significant communication gap until these children learn sign language at school."
